&lt;li&gt;Develop and own the UAE, KSA and Egypt GTM strategy across the Big 6 holding groups including annual JBPs, reseller models, and multi-market expansion plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and evangelize Careem Ads&#39; value proposition - equip agencies with the narrative, data, and proof points to pitch Careem Ads confidently to clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage strategic relationships with agency leadership and own a defined agency revenue pipeline target&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Lead &amp;amp; Mentor the Agency Partnerships Function&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and develop a growing team of Agency Partner Managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive excellence in pipeline planning, forecasting, relationship mapping, and quarterly business reviews (QBRs)Establish the operating rhythm, success metrics, and governance for the function (e.g. pipeline coverage, solution adoption goals, roadshows, JBP attainment)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Drive Enterprise-Level Revenue Growth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influence Careem Ads&#39; revenue plan for non-endemic businesses by scaling agency-led buying unlocking multimillion-dollar contributions through structured partnerships, playbooks, and new channel expansion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver revenue directly across your agency portfolio and identify untapped growth opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to shaping our scalable sales enablement material and run agency roadshows&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Shape Product + Market Fit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead strategic feedback to Product, Measurement, Creative Ops, and Finance - guiding prioritization of formats, measurement solutions, and reporting needs for agencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive agency demand for new innovation and beta pilots&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;5. Be a Foundational Builder&lt;/h4&gt;
