&lt;li&gt;Run team learning and knowledge-sharing sessions — circulating Oracle upgrade documentation,&amp;nbsp;RPA/AI automation demos, and OIC/OCI technical material — to build capability across the&amp;nbsp;department.&lt;/li&gt;
