&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the Category Manager in executing category strategies aligned with business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in sourcing new products and maintaining the assortment for the category.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with suppliers to gather product details, pricing, promotional offers, and manage day-to-day communication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track performance of your category – including sales, pricing, and stock availability – and flag risks or opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help plan and execute weekly and monthly promotions in collaboration with suppliers and internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate and timely listing of products, content, and images on the app in coordination with the content team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise with the supply chain team to support availability, smooth onboarding of new SKUs, and replenishment cycles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct market research to

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Careem is building the Everything App for the greater Middle East — making it easy to move around, order food and groceries, manage payments, and more. Our purpose is simple: to simplify and improve people’s lives and build an awesome organisation that inspires.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Since 2012, Careem has enabled earnings for over 2.5 million Captains, simplified the lives of more than 70 million customers, and built a platform where the region’s best talent and entrepreneurs thrive. We operate in 70+ cities across 10 countries, from Morocco to Pakistan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;We’re now entering our next chapter — one powered by AI. We’re looking for AI talent: curious problem-solvers who know how to apply AI to build tools, automate workflows, and create real impact. Whether it’s streamlining operations, enhancing customer experience, or reimagining internal systems — we want people who can make Careem work smarter and move faster.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Careem Grocery is on a mission to reinvent the way people shop for grocery, pharmacy and retail products. As an exciting new vertical within Careem (a startup within a startup), we’re in the early stages of building our product and have plenty of interesting and fundamental challenges to solve in order to achieve our ambitious growth goals in this burgeoning space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Category Manager, you’ll be responsible for driving our strategies on assortment by defining our selection by store and working with other teams on sourcing, pricing and promotions across our markets for categories. This is a unique role with the opportunity to create genuine impact for the lives of everyday people in our region. We’re looking for someone with solid experience in procuring and managing the entire supply chain of products to ensure we provide the best quality products at the right price.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and lead the product line for Careem Groceries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design the go to market strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the team on maintaining the selection strategy in alignment with the overall department &amp;amp; business strategy and requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the team to identify the selection which need to be sourced within the categories.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and sourcing key consumer trends in online grocery /Q-commerce business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Source &amp;amp; negotiate the required selection with the best prices, quality and minimum MOQ that meets the business objectives, and ensure a competitive commercial terms with the suppliers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the merchandising team to ensure the success of the launched campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the supply chain team to ensure the stock availability and smooth onboarding of the new added items.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the pricing team in sourcing competitive prices to maintain the category profitability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the supplier and maintain the relationship with them through business reviews and growth planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the category assistant to ensure the hygiene of the item&#39;s content and maintain the right visibility on the App.&lt;/li&gt;
