&lt;li&gt;Lead the GTM, and product launches post development till full scale up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the user funnel with data insights to define and inform the roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the setup of touch points throughout, in and outside the Careem app.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the management of all growth touchpoints across the super-app (banners, widgets, shortcuts, vertical tile), Careem Plus loyalty surfaces, and marketing channels.&lt;/li&gt;
