&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;As the Sales Team Lead for Careem, you will be responsible for driving new restaurant partnerships across UAE, with a strong focus on Dubai. Your leadership will be instrumental in motivating and guiding our sales team to achieve ambitious growth targets. Your expertise in sales strategy, team management, and market insights will play a pivotal role in shaping our success across this key market.&lt;/p&gt;
